expected_sql: SELECT DRUG_TYPE, COUNT(*) AS cnt FROM PRESCRIPTIONS WHERE DRUG_TYPE IS NOT NULL GROUP BY DRUG_TYPE ORDER BY cnt DESC

question: Average doses per 24 hours by drug type

question: Average number of diagnoses per admission

expected_sql: SELECT p.GENDER, COUNT(*) AS cnt FROM ADMISSIONS a JOIN PATIENTS p ON a.SUBJECT_ID = p.SUBJECT_ID WHERE p.GENDER IS NOT NULL GROUP BY p.GENDER ORDER BY cnt DESC

question: Average anchor age by admission type
expected_sql: SELECT a.ADMISSION_TYPE, AVG(p.ANCHOR_AGE) AS avg_age FROM ADMISSIONS a JOIN PATIENTS p ON a.SUBJECT_ID = p.SUBJECT_ID WHERE a.ADMISSION_TYPE IS NOT NULL AND p.ANCHOR_AGE IS NOT NULL GROUP BY a.ADMISSION_TYPE
generated_sql: SELECT ADMISSIONS.ADMISSION_TYPE, AVG(PATIENTS.ANCHOR_YEAR - EXTRACT(YEAR FROM PATIENTS.BIRTHDATE)) AS AVERAGE_AGE FROM ADMISSIONS JOIN PATIENTS ON ADMISSIONS.SUBJECT_ID = PATIENTS.SUBJECT_ID WHERE ADMISSIONS.ADMISSION_TYPE IS NOT NULL AND 1=1 GROUP BY ADMISSIONS.ADMISSION_TYPE

question: Count ICU stays by gender
expected_sql: SELECT p.GENDER, COUNT(*) AS cnt FROM ICUSTAYS i JOIN PATIENTS p ON i.SUBJECT_ID = p.SUBJECT_ID WHERE p.GENDER IS NOT NULL GROUP BY p.GENDER ORDER BY cnt DESC
generated_sql: SELECT PATIENTS.GENDER, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM ICUSTAYS JOIN PATIENTS ON TRANSFERS.SUBJECT_ID = PATIENTS.SUBJECT_ID WHERE PATIENTS.GENDER IS NOT NULL AND TRANSFERS.CAREUNIT = 'ICU' GROUP BY PATIENTS.GENDER ORDER BY CNT DESC
